RVICES AND THE WEBSITE. THE LIMITATIONS IN THIS SECTION WILL APPLY EVEN IF ANY LIMITED REMEDY FAILS OF ITS ESSENTIAL PURPOSE. THE ALLOCATION OF RISK BETWEEN YOU AND WTF WHERE&rsquo;S THE FUN IS AN ESSENTIAL ELEMENT OF THE BASIS OF THE BARGAIN BETWEEN YOU AND WTF WHERE&rsquo;S THE FUN. WTF WHERE&rsquo;S THE FUN&rsquo;S AGGREGATE LIABILITY ARISING OUT OF THESE TERMS OR THE USE OF WTF WHERE&rsquo;S THE FUN SERVICES OR THE WEBSITE WILL NOT EXCEED THE GREATER OF ONE HUNDRED DOLLARS ($100) OR THE AMOUNT YOU HAVE PAID WTF WHERE&rsquo;S THE FUN IN THE PAST TWELVE MONTHS. IN NO EVENT WILL ATTORNEYS\' FEES BE AWARDED OR RECOVERABLE. WTF WHERE&rsquo;S THE FUN&rsquo;S LIABILITY WILL BE LIMITED UNDER THIS PARAGRAPH TO THE FULLEST EXTENT PERMITTED BY APPLICABLE LAW, AND THE PROVISIONS OF THIS PARAGRAPH WILL NOT APPLY TO THE EXTENT APPLICABLE LAW PERMITS THE RECOVERY OF DAMAGES, ATTORNEYS&rsquo; FEES OR COSTS OTHERWISE PROHIBITED UNDER THIS PARAGRAPH. THE PROVISIONS OF THIS PARAGRAPH THAT (A) PROHIBIT DAMAGES TO BE MULTIPLIED OR OTHERWISE INCREASED, (B) IMPOSE A DAMAGES LIMITATION OF THE GREATER OF ONE HUNDRED DOLLARS ($100) OR THE AMOUNT YOU HAVE PAID WTF WHERE&rsquo;S THE FUN IN THE PAST TWELVE MONTHS, AND (C) PROHIBIT THE RECOVERY OF ATTORNEYS&rsquo; FEES AND COSTS, DO NOT APPLY IN CERTAIN STATES, INCLUDING WITHOUT LIMITATION NEW JERSEY, TO CLAIMS BROUGHT UNDER STATUTES PERMITTING SUCH RECOVERY.</p>
<p>o&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Force Majeure: WTF Where&rsquo;s The Fun will not be liable to you for failure to perform any of its obligations under this Agreement to the extent that the failure is caused by reason of Force Majeure.</p>
